      • getModelNumber

        public java.lang.String getModelNumber()
        Returns the scanner device model number. This information will be available only after the scanner is enabled.
        Note: The model number is supported on the Scanner Framework version 3.0.11 or later. This API may return an empty string on some devices. 

         
 Example Usage:
 String model = scanneInfo.getModel();
        Returns:
        Returns the model string
